available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadend_event\"><code>loadend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadstart_event\"><code>loadstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/progress_event\"><code>progress</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>File API 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReaderSync\"><code>FileReaderSync</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>readAsText</code> 方法可以将 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\">Blob</a> 或者 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\">File</a> 对象转根据特殊的编码格式转化为内容 (字符串形式)</p>\n<p>这个方法是异步的，也就是说，只有当执行完成后才能够查看到结果，如果直接查看是无结果的，并返回 undefined</p>\n<p>也就是说必须要挂载 实例下的 onload 或 onloadend 的方法处理转化后的结果</p>\n<p>当转化完成后， <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readyState\">readyState</a> 这个参数就会转换 为 done 即完成态， <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadend_event\">event(\"loadend\")</a> 挂载的事件会被触发，并可以通过事件返回的形参得到中的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader/result\">FileReader.result</a> 属性得到转化后的结果</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\"> instance of FileReader.readAsText(blob[, encoding]);\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"二进制对象\"><code>二进制对象</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\">Blob</a>类型 或 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\">File</a>类型</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"编码类型_可选\">编码类型 (可选)</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>传入一个字符串类型的编码类型，如缺省，则默认为“utf-8”类型</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/FileAPI/#readAsDataText","title":"File API"}],"query":"api.FileReader.readAsText"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.FileReader.readAsText","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsText/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader\">FileReader</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"readAsText 方法可以将 Blob 或者 File 对象转根据特殊的编码格式转化为内容 (字符串形式)","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/filereader/readastext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/filer